\section{Activist directors} \label{sect:act_directors}

\subsection{Descriptive statistics}

While we have data on 531,169 director-firm-years, the more appropriate comparison group for activist directors, for whom we present data in their first year on the board, is their fellow new directors.
We identify 52,149 directors as new directors.
